SenStore::FEMCoordSystem

Overview

interface FEMCoordSystem

Operation Index

getFields
Gets the fields of this FEMCoordSystem object.
setFields
Updates the fields of this FEMCoordSystem object.

Operations

FEMCoordSystemFields getFields()

Gets the fields of this FEMCoordSystem object.

Return Value

FEMCoordSystem object fields

void setFields(FEMCoordSystemFields fields, FieldNameList fieldNames)

Updates the fields of this FEMCoordSystem object. If one or more fields are specified, only the fields listed will be updated, the other fields will be left unchanged. If the field list is empty ALL fields will be updated. The available fields are:

  • AX
  • AY
  • AZ
  • BBY
  • BX
  • BZ
  • Description
  • Mode
  • P1
  • P2
  • P3
  • Type
  • Xorigin
  • Yorigin
  • Zorigin
  • LocalID

Parameters

fields
updated fields structure
fieldNames
a string list with field names to be updated
